PUZZLE 2016-12-28:
You've been asked by the head of the Mathematics department to provide him three lists of students ranked by score:
1. Students whose scores are in the top 25%
2. Students whose scores are in the bottom 25%
3. Students in the "middle."

The table you'll query is names TestScore and contains the following fields:
StudentID (Primary KEy)
StudentName (Varchar)  
Score

Can you provide the queries to get the answers to questions 1-3?

BONUS!

Combine the queries into a single result as follows:
Ranking Student Name Score

Where ranking would be one of three values: Top25, Bottom25, Middle
